      "content": "i mean i know i should see a doctor but i've been so busy and the clinics here are always packed. honestly it's probably just my asthma acting up more because of the pollution or whatever. maybe i just need to take an extra puff of my inhaler when it happens? like, if i just bump up my dosage a bit, would that fix the shortness of breath?",
